	<title><![CDATA[Aligning with the Customer's Needs]]></title>
	<title2><![CDATA[Meeting with Dr. Hayes – Aligning with the Customer's Needs]]></title2>
	<instructions><![CDATA[You are at your meeting with Dr. Hayes at Sunnyside Psychiatry. With you is Dr. Bennett, who has been your main contact at Sunnyside Psychiatry during the past year, as well as Dennis, your co-promote partner.  After establishing rapport, you reviewed the agenda for the meeting.  Now it is time to kick off your discussion with a question. Which question will you ask Dr. Hayes first?]]></instructions>
	<choices>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[1]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[A. During my previous talks with Dr. Bennett, we’ve discussed emerging treatments for depression and the opportunities they may offer for growth.  Can you tell me more about those?]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="20">
				<KPI marks="10"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="-10"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="10"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R2_Intro1]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[2]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[B. With the ongoing healthcare reform and increasing regulations, what issues do you see potentially affecting your practice?]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="-10">
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="-10"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R2_D010_B010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[3]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[C. It sounds like the growth of your practice is your number-one priority.  What kind of resources will you need to manage a larger, more complex practice?]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="-20">
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="-10"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="-10"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R2_D010_C010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[4]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[YES]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[D. From previous conversations with Dr. Bennett, I've learned that you want to continue growing your practice.  What are your short- and long-term goals for achieving that growth?]]></choiceText>
